graphql.query:
mutation ($payload:IamCreateUserInput!)
{
	iamCreateUser (payload:$payload)
	{
		id
		accountId
		surname
		avatar
		email
		mobile
		langId
		username
		password
		rememberToken
		data
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

query ($query:QueryStatement)
{
	iamGetUsers (query: $query)
	{
		id
		accountId
		surname
		avatar
		email
		mobile
		langId
		username
		password
		rememberToken
		data
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}
